## Problem

设方程 $$ 2^x\left|\ln x\right| = 1 $$ 有两个不等的实数根 $$ x_1 $$ 和 $$ x_2 $$, 则

A. $$ x_1 x_2 < 0 $$ \
B. $$ x_1 x_2 = 1 $$ \
C. $$ x_1 x_2 > 1 $$ \
D. $$ 0 < x_1 x_2 < 1 $$ \

<script>document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {katex.render("0 &lt; x_1 x_2 &lt; 1");});</script>

